# MemberManager Project Conventions

- **Stack:** Rails 8.1, Ruby 3.3.11, PostgreSQL 16, Redis 7, Sidekiq 7
- **Frontend:** Bootstrap 5.3 via cssbundling-rails, Stimulus, Turbo, importmap-rails
- **Auth:** OmniAuth with OpenID Connect (Authentik)
- **Testing:** Minitest with fixtures, Capybara + Selenium for system tests
- **Linting:** RuboCop with rubocop-rails plugin — run via `docker compose -f docker-compose.lint.yml run --rm rubocop` (build image with `docker compose -f docker-compose.lint.build.yml build rubocop` when needed)
- **Local dev:** Use compose files: `docker-compose.dev.yml`, `docker-compose.test.yml`, `docker-compose.lint.yml` (see README)
- **CI:** GitHub Actions builds and tests on push/PR to `main`; releases push to `ghcr.io` on version tags

## Key Architectural Patterns

- Service objects live in `app/services/` for external API integrations (Authentik, Google Sheets, Slack, Recharge, PayPal)
- Background jobs use Sidekiq with sidekiq-cron; use plain queue names (no `queue_name_prefix`)
- Pagination uses Pagy with Bootstrap nav helpers
- PDF generation uses Prawn
- Environment config via dotenv-rails (`.env` files)
